### ✅ Day 10 – Method example (sum of array)

**File name:** `day10-method-array-sum.java`

```java
public class Day10MethodArraySum {

    static int sumArray(int[] nums) {
        int sum = 0;
        for (int n : nums) {
            sum += n;
        }
        return sum;
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int[] numbers = {2, 4, 6, 8};
        int result = sumArray(numbers);
        System.out.println("Sum of array = " + result);
    }
}
